<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70B4504004" svcinfotypenbr = "06" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Warning Light Check
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B4504004001">
<title>
ABS Warning Light
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition “ON”.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check that ABS warning light (1) comes ON for about 2 seconds and then goes OFF. If ABS warning light never lights up, go to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B4504009">ABS Warning Light Does Not Come ON after Setting Ignition “ON”</intxref>
. If ABS warning light remains ON and no DTC is stored in ABS control module, go to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B4504010">ABS Warning Light Comes ON Steady</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B450008.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "100.071mm" ver = "01" gw = "154" gh = "267"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.352in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.448in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[A]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Without tachometer
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[B]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
With tachometer
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B4504004002">
<title>
EBD Warning Light (Brake Warning Light)
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Perform this check on a level place.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check brake fluid level. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENAP70B4106001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Pull parking brake lever.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition “ON”.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check that EBD warning light (brake warning light) (1) comes ON. If EBD warning light (brake warning light) never lights up, go to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B4504011">EBD Warning Light (Brake Warning Light) Does Not Come ON after Setting Ignition “ON”</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B450009.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "100.114mm" ver = "01" gw = "154" gh = "267"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.352in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.448in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[A]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Without tachometer
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[B]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
With tachometer
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Release parking brake lever and check that EBD warning light goes OFF. If EBD warning light (brake warning light) remains ON and no DTC is stored in ABS control module, go to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B4504012">EBD Warning Light (Brake Warning Light) Comes ON Steady</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
